query:
SELECT u.id, u.username, u.role, u.account_locked, 
       sp.id as staff_permission_id, sp.user_id as sp_user_id
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN staff_permissions sp ON u.id = sp.user_id
WHERE u.username ILIKE '%why%' OR u.role = 'staff_admin'
ORDER BY u.id;
